                        <div id="page-title">
                            重生计划：新面貌
                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<p>Sophia Light主管的处境岌岌可危。当她被选中去领导一个新的机动特遣部队，一个由诸多强势<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-1')">1</a></sup>异常个体（至少部分如此）所组成的特遣部队之时，其感到压力山大。正如我们目前所看到的那样，这支队伍的招募和统合工作进展缓慢。但Light主管总觉得一支单一的队伍，是Omega-7所遗留下来的最大缺陷。然后她坚持认为，为了让MTF Alpha-9 (&quot;最后希望&quot;) 比一个团队更能发挥作用，需要为突发事件做好准备。在本剧场中，我的的故事就是这么开始的：Light主管正在寻找和招募新成员进入其临时的MTF之中。</p>
<p>与此同时，在黄石公园的地下某处，已经有异常事物开始苏醒。该项目是先前由SCP-076一手导致的重生事件中所遗留下来的，而且，现实并没有真正从那次事故中愈合。</p>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<div style="center no-repeat ; float: center; border: solid 5px #000000; padding: 1px 15px; background:#EEEEEE ; margin: 10px 10px 10px 40px; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.2);">
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/grigori-karpin-s-author-page/yellowstoneC" width="400px" alt="yellowstoneC" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<h3 id="toc0"><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">介绍</span></span></h3>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><em>这里，世界法则自石中产生</em></p>
</div>
<p><strong><a href="/new-faces-overture">新面貌：序章</a></strong><br />
by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/redredred" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5379342); return false;">redredred</a></span><br />
<em>这有一部分是真的，但Anne并不知道那是什么。也许这不成问题。</em></p>
<hr />
<h3 id="toc1"><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">到来</span></span></h3>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><em>这里，既新又熟悉的面孔遇到了问题</em></p>
</div>
<p><strong><a href="/recruitment-drive">招募行动</a></strong><br />
by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nagiros" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4665703); return false;">Nagiros</a></span><br />
<em>&quot;我希望你能拯救世界，Light主管。&quot;</em></p>
<p><strong><a class="newpage" href="/welcome-to-yellowstone">Welcome to Yellowstone</a></strong><br />
by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4558017); return false;">Grigori Karpin</a></span><br />
<em>“何意大地在颤动？何意天堂梦中醒？道法自然，毋须缘由。如今正是多难之秋。”</em></p>
<p><strong><a class="newpage" href="/a-team-you-can-maybe-trust">A Team You Can (Maybe) Trust</a></strong><br />
by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5045819); return false;">Calibri Bold</a></span><br />
<em>&quot;你是说你甚至还没觉察到那？以前我们只有亚伯和Iris这么点问题，现在看看你还有什么。&quot;</em><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<p><strong><a class="newpage" href="/jolly-cooperation">Jolly Cooperation</a></strong><br />
by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4558017); return false;">Grigori Karpin</a></span><br />
<em>&quot;You humans are always betraying one another. Amazes me that civilization hasn’t crumbled long before now.&quot;</em></p>
<p><strong><a class="newpage" href="/light-and-the-mole">Light and the Mole</a></strong><br />
by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4558017); return false;">Grigori Karpin</a></span><br />
<em>“Oh look, a manhunt! You favorite!”</em></p>
<p><strong><a class="newpage" href="/gomboc">Gömböc</a></strong><br />
by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/redredred" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5379342); return false;">redredred</a></span><br />
<em>There was no alarm.</em></p>
<p><strong><a class="newpage" href="/bottom-floor">Bottom Floor</a></strong><br />
by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4558017); return false;">Grigori Karpin</a></span><br />
<em>A fulcrum! A universal pry bar, to crack open the weight of millennia worth of constant observations by the beings of this universe. Such that, the incredible becomes mundane. And the mundane becomes the impossible.</em></p>
<p><strong><a class="newpage" href="/truth-lies">Truth Lies</a></strong><br />
by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5045819); return false;">Calibri Bold</a></span><br />
<em>&quot;Does this mean we're friends?&quot;</em></p>
<hr />
<h3 id="toc2"><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">结尾</span></span></h3>
<p><em>in which our events come to a close and our characters deal with the ramifications of all they've seen.</em></p>
<p><strong><a class="newpage" href="/shut-it-down">Shut It Down</a></strong><br />
by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4558017); return false;">Grigori Karpin</a></span><br />
<em>We don’t have any more options, Sophia. Look… I’m giving you another hour and then I’m taking these people out of here. You can stay if you want.</em><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<p><strong><a class="newpage" href="/tangled-web">Tangled Web</a></strong><br />
by <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4558017); return false;">Grigori Karpin</a></span><br />
<em>Let me be clear, the following briefing is not to leave this room. In fact, I’ve already activated a memetic agent on all of you to stop you from repeating it.</em></p>
<hr />
<p><em><strong>现在&#8230;&#8230;结束了！</strong></em></p>
<hr />
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><a href="/resurrection"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/resurrection/resurrection%283%29.png" width="600px" alt="resurrection%283%29.png" class="image" /></a></div>
</div>
</div>
